<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,267,1793,1819]" pageId="5" pageNumber="540">Remarks.</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Desmarest, A. G." box="[273,528,1793,1819]" pageId="5" pageNumber="540" pagination="138 - 425" refId="ref5532" refString="Desmarest, A. G. (1823) Malacostraces. In: Dictionnaire des sciences naturelles, dans lequel on traite methodiquement des differens etres de la nature, consideres soit en eux-memes, d'apres l'etat actuel de nos connoissances, soit relativement a l'utilite qu'en peuvent retirer la medecine, l'agriculture, le commerce et les artes. Suivi d'une biographie des plus celebres naturalistes ... Strasbourg, Paris, 28, 138 - 425." type="journal article" year="1823">Desmarest (1823: 228)</bibRefCitation>
narrated the erection of the genus by W. E. Leach based on his unpublished work. 
<bibRefCitation author="Guinot, D." box="[151,369,1828,1855]" pageId="5" pageNumber="540" pagination="540 - 563" refId="ref5647" refString="Guinot, D. (1967) Recherches preliminaires sur les groupements naturels chez les Crustaces Decapods Brachyoures. III. A propos des affinites des Genres Dairoides Stebbing et Daira de Haan. Bulletin du Museum National d' Histoire Naturelle, Paris, Series 2, 39 (3), 540 - 563." type="journal article" year="1967">Guinot (1967: 559)</bibRefCitation>
designated 
<taxonomicName authority="(Linnaeus, 1758)" baseAuthorityName="Linnaeus" baseAuthorityYear="1758" box="[504,811,1828,1855]" class="Malacostraca" family="Xanthidae" genus="Zosimus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="5" pageNumber="540" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="aeneus">
<emphasis box="[504,520,1830,1855]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="540">Z</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[534,612,1830,1855]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="540">aeneus</emphasis>
(Linnaeus, 1758)
</taxonomicName>
as the only species for the genus but suggested conservatively to include 
<taxonomicName authority="(A. Milne Edwards, 1867)" baseAuthorityName="A. Milne Edwards" baseAuthorityYear="1867" box="[374,941,1865,1892]" class="Malacostraca" family="Xanthidae" genus="Platypodia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="5" pageNumber="540" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="actaeoides">
<emphasis box="[374,627,1865,1891]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="540">Platypodia actaeoides</emphasis>
(A. Milne Edwards, 1867)
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authority="(De Man, 1887)" baseAuthorityName="De Man" baseAuthorityYear="1887" box="[955,1386,1865,1891]" class="Malacostraca" family="Xanthidae" genus="Platypodia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="5" pageNumber="540" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="maculata">
<emphasis box="[955,1192,1865,1891]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="540">Platypodia maculata</emphasis>
(De 
<bibRefCitation author="Man, J. G. de" box="[1253,1378,1865,1891]" pageId="5" pageNumber="540" pagination="215 - 288" refId="ref5822" refString="Man, J. G. de (1887) Bericht uber die von Herrn Dr. J. Brock im indischenArchipel gesammelten Decapoden und Stomatopoden. Archiv fur Naturgeschichte, 53 (2), 215 - 288, pls. 7 - 10. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. part. 4747" type="journal article" year="1887">Man, 1887</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authority="Rathbun, 1906" authorityName="Rathbun" authorityYear="1906" box="[151,546,1901,1927]" class="Malacostraca" family="Xanthidae" genus="Actaea" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="5" pageNumber="540" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hawaiiensis">
<emphasis box="[151,369,1901,1927]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="540">Actaea hawaiiensis</emphasis>
Rathbun, 1906
</taxonomicName>
. 
<bibRefCitation author="Ng, P. K. L. &amp; Guinot, D. &amp; Davie, P. J. F." box="[558,797,1901,1927]" pageId="5" pageNumber="540" pagination="1 - 208" refId="ref5953" refString="Ng, P. K. L., Guinot, D. &amp; Davie, P. J. F. (2008) Systema Brachyurorum: Part I. An annotated checklist of extant brachyuran crabs of the world. The Raffles Bulletin of Zoology, 17, 1 - 208." type="journal article" year="2008">
Ng 
<emphasis box="[600,650,1901,1927]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="540">et al</emphasis>
. (2008: 210)
</bibRefCitation>
moved 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Rathbun" authorityYear="1906" box="[889,1053,1901,1927]" class="Malacostraca" family="Xanthidae" genus="Actaea" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="5" pageNumber="540" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hawaiiensis">
<emphasis box="[889,906,1901,1927]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="540">A</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[921,1053,1901,1927]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="540">hawaiiensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authority="A. Milne Edwards, 1867" authorityName="A. Milne Edwards" authorityYear="1867" genus="Lophactaea" kingdom="Animalia" pageId="5" pageNumber="540" rank="species" species="actaeoides">
<emphasis box="[1068,1328,1901,1927]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="540">Lophactaea actaeoides</emphasis>
A. Milne Edwards, 1867
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authority="Henderson, 1893" authorityName="Henderson" authorityYear="1893" box="[338,625,1937,1963]" genus="Lophactaea" kingdom="Animalia" pageId="5" pageNumber="540" rank="species" species="fissa">
<emphasis box="[338,354,1938,1963]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="540">L</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[370,421,1937,1963]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="540">fissa</emphasis>
Henderson, 1893
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicName authority="De Man, 1887" authorityName="De Man" authorityYear="1887" box="[635,950,1937,1963]" class="Malacostraca" family="Xanthidae" genus="Platypodia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="5" pageNumber="540" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="maculata">
<emphasis box="[635,651,1938,1963]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="540">L</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[667,771,1937,1963]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="540">maculata</emphasis>
De 
<bibRefCitation author="Man, J. G. de" box="[823,950,1937,1963]" pageId="5" pageNumber="540" pagination="215 - 288" refId="ref5822" refString="Man, J. G. de (1887) Bericht uber die von Herrn Dr. J. Brock im indischenArchipel gesammelten Decapoden und Stomatopoden. Archiv fur Naturgeschichte, 53 (2), 215 - 288, pls. 7 - 10. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. part. 4747" type="journal article" year="1887">Man, 1887</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, and 
<taxonomicName authority="Herbst, 1794" authorityName="Herbst" authorityYear="1794" box="[1013,1357,1937,1963]" class="Malacostraca" family="Cancridae" genus="Cancer" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="5" pageNumber="540" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="sculptus">
<emphasis box="[1013,1197,1937,1963]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="540">Cancer sculptus</emphasis>
Herbst, 1794
</taxonomicName>
, to the genus on the basis of their proposed generic characters of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Leach in Desmarest" authorityYear="1823" box="[797,890,1974,1999]" class="Malacostraca" family="Xanthidae" genus="Zosimus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="5" pageNumber="540" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[797,890,1974,1999]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="540">Zosimus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. Currently, the genus consists of the above-mentioned 6 species and a questionable species, 
<taxonomicName authority="Dana, 1852" authorityName="Dana" authorityYear="1852" box="[649,954,2008,2035]" class="Malacostraca" family="Xanthidae" genus="Zosimus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="5" pageNumber="540" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="laevis">
<emphasis box="[649,815,2009,2035]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="540">Zosimus laevis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Dana, J. D." box="[822,954,2008,2035]" pageId="5" pageNumber="540" pagination="73 - 86" refId="ref5371" refString="Dana, J. D. (1852) Conspectus Crustaceorum, etc. Conspectus of the Crustacea of the Exploring Expedition under Capt Wilkes, U. S. N., including the Crustacea Cancroidea Corystoidea. Proceedings of the Academy of Natural Sciences of Philadelphia, 6, 73 - 86." type="journal article" year="1852">Dana, 1852</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, which has been named as 
<taxonomicName box="[1258,1436,2009,2035]" genus="Zozymus" kingdom="Animalia" pageId="5" pageNumber="540" rank="species" species="laevis">
<emphasis box="[1258,1436,2009,2035]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="540">Zozymus laevis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in the original description (
<bibRefCitation author="Dana, J. D." box="[452,620,152,179]" pageId="6" pageNumber="541" pagination="73 - 86" refId="ref5371" refString="Dana, J. D. (1852) Conspectus Crustaceorum, etc. Conspectus of the Crustacea of the Exploring Expedition under Capt Wilkes, U. S. N., including the Crustacea Cancroidea Corystoidea. Proceedings of the Academy of Natural Sciences of Philadelphia, 6, 73 - 86." type="journal article" year="1852">Dana 1852: 77</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Ng, P. K. L. &amp; Guinot, D. &amp; Davie, P. J. F." box="[632,850,153,180]" pageId="6" pageNumber="541" pagination="1 - 208" refId="ref5953" refString="Ng, P. K. L., Guinot, D. &amp; Davie, P. J. F. (2008) Systema Brachyurorum: Part I. An annotated checklist of extant brachyuran crabs of the world. The Raffles Bulletin of Zoology, 17, 1 - 208." type="journal article" year="2008">
Ng 
<emphasis box="[672,721,153,179]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="541">et al</emphasis>
. 2008: 206
</bibRefCitation>
). In 
<collectingCountry box="[898,983,153,179]" name="Taiwan" pageId="6" pageNumber="541">Taiwan</collectingCountry>
, only 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Linnaeus" baseAuthorityYear="1758" box="[1050,1157,153,179]" class="Malacostraca" family="Xanthidae" genus="Zosimus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="6" pageNumber="541" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="aeneus">
<emphasis box="[1050,1066,154,179]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="541">Z</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[1079,1157,154,179]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="541">aeneus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
has been reported (
<bibRefCitation author="Ng, P. K. L. &amp; Shih, H. - T. &amp; Ho, P. - H. &amp; Wang, C. - H." pageId="6" pageNumber="541" pagination="1010 - 1683" refId="ref6007" refString="Ng, P. K. L., Shih, H. - T., Ho, P. - H. &amp; Wang, C. - H. (2017) An updated annotated checklist of brachyuran crabs from Taiwan (Crustacea: Decapoda). Journal of the National Taiwan Museum, 70 (3 - 4), 1010 - 1683." type="journal article" year="2017">
Ng 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="541">et al</emphasis>
. 2017
</bibRefCitation>
). The present finding of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="De Man" authorityYear="1887" box="[522,656,189,215]" class="Malacostraca" family="Xanthidae" genus="Platypodia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="6" pageNumber="541" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="maculata">
<emphasis box="[522,538,190,215]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="541">Z</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[552,656,189,215]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="541">maculata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
represents the first record of this species for 
<collectingCountry box="[1160,1246,189,215]" name="Taiwan" pageId="6" pageNumber="541">Taiwan</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
